#. Tag: title
#: hacking.docbook:2
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hacking &appname;"
msgstr "&appname; varjatumad võimalused"

#. Tag: para
#: hacking.docbook:4
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the spirit of Free Software, you are welcome to hack on &appname; as much "
"as you like. You should be able to write scripts to import, export, or "
"modify data very easily. This chapter gives you more information about doing "
"that."
msgstr ""
"Vaba tarkvara vaimus oled kutsutud &appname;t just sel moel muutma, nagu sa "
"seda ise soovid. Väga lihtne on kirjutada skripte andmete importimiseks, "
"eksportimiseks või muutmiseks. Käesolevas peatükis seda ja muud "
"tutvustataksegi."

#. Tag: title
#: hacking.docbook:9
#, no-c-format
msgid "File Format"
msgstr "Failivorming"

#. Tag: para
#: hacking.docbook:11
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The default &appname; data file is a zip archive, normally with a <literal "
"role=\"extension\">.tc</literal> file extension. Inside the archive is a top-"
"level <filename>tellico.xml</filename> file. Images may be included inside "
"the <filename>images/</filename> folder in the archive, or they may be "
"included in the &XML; data directly in a base64 encoding. Images may also be "
"saved inside the application data folder, in which case, they are not in the "
"data file at all. &appname; can also load the &XML; file, by itself, "
"uncompressed."
msgstr ""
"&appname; vaikimisi andmefail on zip-arhiiv, tavaliselt faililaiendiga "
"<literal role=\"extension\">.tc</literal>. Arhiivis asub tipptasemel fail "
"<filename>tellico.xml</filename>. Pildid võib panna arhiivi kataloogi "
"<filename>images/</filename>, kuid need võib ka lisada base64 kodeeringus "
"otse &XML;-andmetesse. Samuti võib pildid salvestada rakenduse "
"andmekataloogi, millisel juhul neid ei leidu üldse andmefailis. &appname; "
"võib laadida ka tihendamata &XML;-faili."

#. Tag: title
#: hacking.docbook:16
#, no-c-format
msgid "&XML; Data"
msgstr "&XML;-andmed"

#. Tag: title
#: hacking.docbook:22
#, no-c-format
msgid "Collection"
msgstr "Kogu"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: hacking.docbook:23
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<![CDATA[\n"
"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n"
"<!DOCTYPE tellico PUBLIC \"-//Robby Stephenson/DTD Tellico V11.0//EN\" "
"\"http://periapsis.org/tellico/dtd/v11/tellico.dtd\">\n"
"<tellico xmlns=\"http://periapsis.org/tellico/\" syntaxVersion=\"11\">\n"
" <collection title=\"My Books\" type=\"2\">\n"
" </collection>\n"
"</tellico>\n"
"]]>"
msgstr ""
"<![CDATA[\n"
"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n"
"<!DOCTYPE tellico PUBLIC \"-//Robby Stephenson/DTD Tellico V11.0//EN\" "
"\"http://periapsis.org/tellico/dtd/v11/tellico.dtd\">\n"
"<tellico xmlns=\"http://periapsis.org/tellico/\" syntaxVersion=\"11\">\n"
" <collection title=\"Minu raamatud\" type=\"2\">\n"
" </collection>\n"
"</tellico>\n"
"]]>"

#. Tag: para
#: hacking.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The file begins with the required &XML; declaration and encoding, followed "
"by the doctype. When a new field type is added or additional properties are "
"set on the default fields, the doctype DTD version is incremented. &appname; "
"is always able to open and read any previous DTD version, but will save "
"files in the current version. The DTD location does point to an actual DTD "
"file."
msgstr ""
"Fail algab nõutava &XML;-deklaratsiooni ja kodeeringuga, millele järgneb "
"doctype. Kui lisatakse uus väljatüüp või vaikeväljadele määratakse "
"lisaomadusi, suurendatakse doctype DTD versiooni. &appname; võib alati avada "
"ja lugeda varasemaid DTD versioone, kuid salvestab failid aktiivsesse "
"versiooni. DTD asukoht viitab tegelikule DTD-failile."

#. Tag: para
#: hacking.docbook:29
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The top-level element is a <markup>&lt;tellico&gt;</markup> element, "
"containing the default namespace declaration and the syntax version of the "
"file, which should always match the DTD."
msgstr ""
"Tipptaseme element on <markup>&lt;tellico&gt;</markup>, mis sisaldab "
"vaikimisi nimeruumi deklaratsiooni ja faili süntaksi versiooni, mis peab "
"alati klappima DTD-ga."

#. Tag: para
#: hacking.docbook:33
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <markup>&lt;tellico&gt;</markup> element contains one <markup>&lt;"
"collection&gt;</markup> element. Multiple collections are ignored, for now. "
"The <markup>title</markup> attribute contains the collection title, while "
"the <markup>type</markup> specifies what kinds of entries are contained in "
"the collection. The allowable types are in <link linkend=\"collection-type-"
"values\">listed in a later section</link>. An optional <markup>entryTitle</"
"markup> attribute may be used to specify the title of the entries for a "
"custom collection, and should be plural."
msgstr ""
"Element <markup>&lt;tellico&gt;</markup> sisaldab üht elementi <markup>&lt;"
"collection&gt;</markup>. Praegu eiratakse mitut kogu. Atribuut "
"<markup>title</markup> sisaldab kogu pealkirja, <markup>type</markup> aga "
"määrab, millist laadi kirjed sisalduvad kogus. Lubatud tüübid on <link "
"linkend=\"collection-type-values\">ära toodud allpool</link>. Atribuuti "
"<markup>entryTitle</markup> võib soovi korral kasutada kohandatud kogu "
"kirjete pealkirja määramiseks ning see peab olema mitmuses."

