#. Tag: title
#: hacking.docbook:205
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hidden Configuration Options"
msgstr "Peidetud seadistusvalikud"

#. Tag: para
#: hacking.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&appname; has some additional configuration options that are not visible in "
"the <interface>Configuration Dialog</interface>. They are not important "
"enough to warrant cluttering the dialog with more settings, but as they "
"represent options which may appeal to various users, the application does "
"read them from the configuration file."
msgstr ""
"&appname;l on ka mõned seadistusvalikud, mida ei ole näha "
"<interface>seadistustedialoogis</interface>. Need ei ole nii tähtsad, et "
"muuta nendega niigi rohkete valikutega dialooge veel keerulisemaks, aga et "
"nad võivad siiski olla teatavatele kasutajatele vajalikud või tulusad, annab "
"rakendus võimaluse muuta neid otse seadistustefailis ja neid seejärel ka ära "
"kasutada."

#. Tag: para
#: hacking.docbook:211
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The settings for &appname; are saved in a file in the user's home folder, "
#| "namely <filename>$<envar>KDEHOME</envar>/share/config/tellicorc</"
#| "filename>. Within that file, settings are put in groups, which appear "
#| "with bracketed names, such as [General Options]. To add a setting to the "
#| "<emphasis>General Options</emphasis> group, find the line in the settings "
#| "file with that group name. If it does not appear, then create it yourself "
#| "by adding a line saying [General Options]. Then, the setting can be added "
#| "underneath the group name."
msgid ""
"The settings for &appname; are saved in a file in the user's home folder, "
"typically <filename>~/.config/tellicorc</filename>. Within that file, "
"settings are put in groups, which appear with bracketed names, such as "
"[General Options]. To add a setting to the <emphasis>General Options</"
"emphasis> group, find the line in the settings file with that group name. If "
"it does not appear, then create it yourself by adding a line saying [General "
"Options]. Then, the setting can be added underneath the group name."
msgstr ""
"&appname; seadistused salvestatakse kasutaja kodukataloogi, täpsemalt faili "
"<filename>$<envar>KDEHOME</envar>/share/config/tellicorc</filename>. Failis "
"on seadistused jagatud rühmadesse, mille nimetused on nurksulgudes, näiteks "
"[General Options]. Seadistuse lisamiseks mainitud <emphasis>üldiste "
"valikute</emphasis> rühma otsi kõigepealt seadistusfailist üles vastava "
"rühma nimega rida. Kui seda ei ole, lisa ise rida, millele seisab [General "
"Options]. Seejärel saab vajaliku seadistuse lisada rühma nime alla."

